Note que os valores de venda acima já estão quando venda em atacado, até porque lembrancinhas tendem a ser vendidas em grandes quantidades (mais que 10). Abaixo algumas imagens da lembrancinha da Bailarina pronta:    <img class="aligncenter" src="https://dj32nvn913e95.cloudfront.net/image/gallery/original/q9ciu6iuhjqntcg3bb1ebrgqo71761f18de2398ca08087b548da4098e4.jpg" alt="bailarina-01.jpg" width="271" height="361" data-cke-saved-src="https://dj32nvn913e95.cloudfront.net/image/gallery/original/q9ciu6iuhjqntcg3bb1ebrgqo71761f18de2398ca08087b548da4098e4.jpg" /><img class="aligncenter" src="https://dj32nvn913e95.cloudfront.net/image/gallery/original/q9ciu6iuhjqntcg3bb1ebrgqo74fc0faec54922417e17e761a8042330d.jpg" alt="bailarina-02.jpg" width="266" height="355" data-cke-saved-src="https://dj32nvn913e95.cloudfront.net/image/gallery/original/q9ciu6iuhjqntcg3bb1ebrgqo74fc0faec54922417e17e761a8042330d.jpg" /><img class="aligncenter" src="https://dj32nvn913e95.cloudfront.net/image/gallery/original/q9ciu6iuhjqntcg3bb1ebrgqo790169d2af10e49c276ab08cacce38b6f.jpg" alt="bailarina-03.jpg" width="266" height="355" data-cke-saved-src="https://dj32nvn913e95.cloudfront.net/image/gallery/original/q9ciu6iuhjqntcg3bb1ebrgqo790169d2af10e49c276ab08cacce38b6f.jpg" />

