<ul>
 	<li>30 cm de fita branca de cetim ou de nylon com 10 mm de largura;</li>
 	<li>EVAs nas cores:
<ul>
 	<li>01 x preto com glitter;</li>
 	<li>01 x branco com glitter;</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<img class="aligncenter" src="https://dj32nvn913e95.cloudfront.net/image/gallery/original/r856mlk79bq23jd3olas0dm4900b22ce00e994a26d5c0b5b2910c5dc27.jpg" alt="materiais.jpg" data-cke-saved-src="https://dj32nvn913e95.cloudfront.net/image/gallery/original/r856mlk79bq23jd3olas0dm4900b22ce00e994a26d5c0b5b2910c5dc27.jpg" />
